rComments: This is how classes should be.  Presented material in an interesting manner, with more emphasis on learning than testing your knowledge.  If you can take his class, do it.
Fun, interesting, my favorite GE professor.
One of the best teacher I have had.  There is less focus on grades and more on content and learning.

One of the best teachers I have had in my whole life. If you can take decision analysis with Prof Abbas, be prepared to change the way you think about decisions for ever. Right on. Go Professor. Best class I've taken

This guy is a really good teacher. His tests and homeworks are pretty much straight forward. He has a really east grading scale. Material is presented well and pretty interesting. If you can have Ali as your teacher, then do so. He is a good guy.
